  <description><![CDATA[<p>Summit Lodge Boutique Hotel Whistler is a fun boutique hotel for your next escape to the Whistler Mountains. With an eye for all “the little things”, Summit is perfectly tailored to the traveler who finds joy in life's everyday moments. Summit makes it easier for their guests to enjoy all the adventures Whistler has to offer by providing complimentary perks like wi-fi, shuttle service, pet stays, equipment storage, rent a fish, free hot beverage bar and complimentary use of snowshoes. What makes our guests keep coming back is that we are distinct, memorable and different, from our rubber duckies to cuddly sock monsters there's a little something for everyone!</p>
<p>The Summit Lodge Boutique Hotel Whistler is located in the heart of it all, steps from shops, restaurants, Whistler marketplace and the world famous Olympic Celebration Plaza. Offering complimentary wireless internet, local and toll free calls, complimentary ski valet/storage and shuttle to and from the lifts or just a 7 minute walk from our front door to the gondola; pets can also stay for free. Relax in our outdoor hot tub and pool backing onto an exclusive forest canopy where our guests can cozy up beside the outdoor fire pit.</p>
<p>Enjoy all the restaurants, bars, nightclubs, shopping and trendy cafes that line the unique pedestrian only village stroll.</p>]]></description>
